# This repo tracks ONLY the Mac Mini wall mount, kept under macmini-wall-mount/.
# The working directory is a shared catch-all, so everything is ignored by
# default and the wall-mount files are added explicitly.
/*
!.gitignore
!.gitattributes
!macmini-wall-mount
macmini-wall-mount/*
!macmini-wall-mount/README.md
!macmini-wall-mount/macmini_wall_mount.scad
!macmini-wall-mount/macmini_wall_mount.stl
!macmini-wall-mount/Macmini.glb
!macmini-wall-mount/versions/
!macmini-wall-mount/docs/

# Project-wide design docs (methodology + specs)
!docs

# Feature-first CAD engine (local package)
!tools

# Temp preview renders
macmini-wall-mount/v_*.png
*.echo
